Create a ~/REPOSITORIES direcotry and download CAP and GEOTOOLS inside it. These are private repositories so you will need permisson from Carl Tape (ctape@alaska.edu)

> mkdir ~/REPOSITORIES/

%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PREREQUISITE

0. Install cap (https://github.com/uafseismo/capuaf)

> cd ~/REPOSITORIES/
> git clone --depth=1 https://GITHUBUSERNAME@github.com/uafseismo/capuaf.git capuaf
> cd capuaf
> make all

1. Get a copy of pyseis (https://github.com/uafseismo/pyseis)
> cd ~/REPOSITORIES/
> git clone --depth=1 https://GITHUBUSERNAME@github.com/uafseismo/pyseis.git pyseis

%------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DATA EXTRACTION and RUNNING CAP
- See README_SilwalTape2016 for Anchorage event